metadata.description: The Collective : Land is a collection of unique NFT Lands that grant the owner access to a token gated microverse. Each land is distinct and grants exclusive access to a digital world teeming with opportunity. Explore and customize your own piece of the microverse. With ongoing updates and new features, The Collective : Land collection is an ever-evolving investment that grants you access to an immersive digital universe.
metadata.name: The Collective : Land #1
